reviewText: One woman has sex with multiple different men, but not at the same time. The woman has ugly fake breasts and is bald.

I just watched this and I loved it.  The story line was silly at some points but that made it funny.  The sex scenes were hot.  Especially the gay scene towards the begining!  I wish it was easier, and cheaper, to find porn like this.  This movie did it all for me and I am lookng forward to seeing other movies with the same leading woman.
